{"tid":2347574,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"國際組織：港人活於恐懼","createTime":"2020-12-31T06:59:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-31T07:02:39.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"53ed67831f6ab7dd7771bd782432159e9f03b205","tid":2347574,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T06:59:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201231/NK4GKAYKEREZFHP4ONTZ7AVVSU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201231%2FNK4GKAYKEREZFHP4ONTZ7AVVSU%2F&d=BLGvZshAgiFYydKSMDjJm5nDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=c28b9269\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201231%2FNK4GKAYKEREZFHP4ONTZ7AVVSU%2F&h=25fc6b24\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201231/NK4GKAYKEREZFHP4ONTZ7AVVSU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n國際組織：港人活於恐懼<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/M10c6Ol9mX-LavS3V7oGO_7QAec=/1000x562/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VGQRAU2G2BDWNDMBSK4GC72JMY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FM10c6Ol9mX-LavS3V7oGO_7QAec%3D%2F1000x562%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVGQRAU2G2BDWNDMBSK4GC72JMY.jpg&h=6eee993c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n國際特赦組織亞太區域主任Yamini Mishra<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】12港人經「秘密審判」判刑後，引起國際社會極大迴響，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：法院：「上家」策劃偷渡  10港人囚7月至3年<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n憂判囚港青遭虐待<br />\n<br />\nYamini Mishra回應判決時指，判決是在不公平審訊下作出，12港人被剝奪選擇法律代表、為他們辯護的權利，多位受家屬委託的內地律師代表也遭中國當局恐嚇，被要求退出案件，外交人員、記者和家屬均無法出席本周一的閉門聆訊。她直言，一眾被判刑的港青將來在中國監獄裏，仍可能面對被酷刑或其他虐待，「中國當局再一次向世界展示，抗爭者不會獲得公平審訊」。<br />\n<br />\nHKDC朱牧民稱，為12位港人和其家屬面對的情況感到痛心，「他們（12人）在海中受折磨、128天的專制扣留、不能與家人和自己選擇的律師聯絡，被迫寫認罪書，如今還要面對在內地的監獄，一切也是因為他們希望自由」。<br />\n<br />\n他指，香港司法制度。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"28d2d4db25eae68538afd874db03cecb9320611f","tid":2347574,"uid":275498,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T07:02:39.000Z","msg":"左:  港人活於恐懼<br />\n右:  港豬樂於炒賣<br />\n橫:  痴呆同體 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}